  ],
  "notes": "Across all 26276 pages sampled, this component has a single identical structure with no variation (duplicates: 14, textVaries: false). All content — award images, their hrefs and alt text, and all social media links — is hardcoded. The awards section contains three fixed links to rankings and the Queen's Anniversary Prize. The social section contains six fixed social media icons (Instagram, LinkedIn, TikTok, Bluesky, Threads, Weibo). The inner `.region.region-footer_last` and `.block` wrappers are CMS layout artifacts and should be simplified in the React implementation. No props are needed.",
  "htmlExamples": [
    "<div class=\"footicons\">\n  <div class=\"awards\">\n    <a href=\"//www.sheffield.ac.uk/about/rankings\"><img src=\"/themes/custom/common/uos/images/WORLD100_stamp_white.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"A World Top 100 University\"></a>\n    <a href=\"//www.sheffield.ac.uk/about/rankings\"><img src=\"/themes/custom/common/uos/images/russell.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Russell Group\"></a>\n    <a href=\"//www.sheffield.ac.uk/about/queens-prize\"><img src=\"/themes/custom/common/uos/images/QAP.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Five Queen's Anniversary Prizes\"></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"region region-footer_last\">\n    <div class=\"social\">\n      <a href=\"https://instagram.com/theuniversityofsheffield\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"//cdn.sheffield.ac.uk/sites/default/files/styles/original/public/2022-10/social-in.png?itok=UpurzD83\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\" alt=\"Instagram logo\"></a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/school/university-of-sheffield/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"//cdn.sheffield.ac.uk/sites/default/files/styles/original/public/2022-10/social-li.png?itok=pBCn-VE3\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\" alt=\"LinkedIn\"></a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@sheffielduni\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"//cdn.sheffield.ac.uk/sites/default/files/styles/original/public/2022-10/social-tt.png?itok=G8v7iLhy\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\" alt=\"TikTok\"></a>\n      <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/sheffielduni.bsky.social\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/original/public/2025-10/social-icon-bluesky2.png?h=ebc76fda&itok=vfSDiDHf\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\" alt=\"Bluesky butterfly logo\"></a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.threads.com/@theuniversityofsheffield\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/original/public/2025-10/social-icon-threads.png?h=ebc76fda&itok=TswsZn-u\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\" alt=\"Threads logo\"></a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/sheffielduni\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"//cdn.sheffield.ac.uk/sites/default/files/styles/original/public/2022-10/social-wb.png?itok=c0RLZdQP\" width=\"34\" height=\"34\" alt=\"Weibo\"></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
